FBIS3-23427 "jptot013__l94108" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 22 March 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Assassination Attempt Against Ingush Justice Minister LD2203115194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1000 GMT 22 Mar 94 LD2203115194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] It was learned today that an attempt was made on the life of the Ingush Republic's justice minister at 2000 on Monday. His car, in which the deputy minister was also a passenger, was shot at from a passing motor vehicle in the settlement of Nizhniye Achaluki. Neither the minister nor his deputy were wounded but the driver was wounded and died in the hospital. An investigative group of the Russian Interior Ministry has started work at the scene of the incident.
